  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"504675874\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"325\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cb04d40b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FrFWVXwibLGtz8W4v935cTPdaS5OMoc0keBicNCThn6m8YDQCJgBHia87iaicNWxXiaMtDfyW53w2MumnU9K6zLVgAN5w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;line-height: 29.75px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mgizcy1nco\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mgizc9iv16kx\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">Chrome 开发者工具</span></span><span leaf=\"\">是一套 Web 开发者工具，直接内置于&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mgizcy111wbd\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-size: 15px;font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;letter-spacing: 0.578px;word-spacing: 0px;text-shadow: none;\">Google Chrome</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;浏览器中，帮助您即时修改页面和快速诊断问题，让您能够更快地构建更好的网站。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;line-height: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mgizczon1p69\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mgizh49gi1c\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;letter-spacing: 0.578px;word-spacing: 0px;text-shadow: none;\">Chrome 开发者工具</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mgizh49gphp\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><a href=\"https://developer.chrome.google.cn/docs/devtools/ai-assistance?hl=zh-cn\" target=\"_blank\">https://developer.chrome.google.cn/docs/devtools/ai-assistance?hl=zh-cn</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;line-height: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mgizd0voc0y\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mgizh49g1j6p\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;letter-spacing: 0.578px;word-spacing: 0px;text-shadow: none;\">Google Chrome</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;line-height: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mgizecboy4y\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mgizh49glog\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;letter-spacing: 0.578px;word-spacing: 0px;text-shadow: none;\"><a href=\"https://www.google.com/chrome/?hl=zh-cn\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/chrome/?hl=zh-cn</a></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjclmwdi1by2\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjclmwds18il\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">在<a class=\"normal_text_link album\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/appmsgalbum?__biz=MzAwODY4OTk2Mg==&amp;action=getalbum&amp;album_id=4201029354031300611&amp;token=841427797&amp;lang=zh_CN#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"Chrome 开发者工具\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">之前的文章</span></a>中，您已经充分了解到，AI 辅助功能可帮助您直接在开发者工具中使用 Gemini 调试样式问题。本文将带您了解这项功能如何通过 5 种出色的方式更轻松地设置网页样式，完成从解析布局到 \"维修飞机\" 的各项任务。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjclnpb21de9\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjclnpbc1uh0\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\">此段屏幕录制内容展示了 AI 辅助功能如何帮助您使用 CSS 动画实现 marquee 效果</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);overflow: hidden;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(83, 98, 242, 0);margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-right: 0%;margin-bottom: 3px;margin-left: 0%;text-align: justify;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;height: auto;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(70, 70, 70);background-color: rgba(84, 98, 242, 0);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 4px 0px inset;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;justify-content: flex-start;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 88%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;\">\n       <div style=\"margin-top: 3px;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;transform: translate3d(-8px, 0px, 0px);text-align: left;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <div style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);text-align: justify;font-size: 20px;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">1. 了解布局</span></strong></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjclp13n1cx7\">在网站开发中，我们很少能完全从零开始。很多时候，您需要基于一套您完全不熟悉的现有代码进行构建，更糟的是，身边可能没有任何人能提供相关背景知识。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjclp13naq\">此时，您可以直接向 AI 提问元素的布局情况，从而理解元素为何以特定方式呈现 (深入到最底层节点)，以及元素上&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\">overflow: hidden;</span>&nbsp;属性存在的真正原因。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjclp13naq\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">建议尝试的提示</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjclqk7d113f\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjclqk7np71\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\">Give me a summary of how this element and its children are laid out and re-create the layout in ASCII.</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);overflow: hidden;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(83, 98, 242, 0);margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-right: 0%;margin-bottom: 3px;margin-left: 0%;text-align: justify;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;height: auto;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(70, 70, 70);background-color: rgba(84, 98, 242, 0);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 4px 0px inset;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;justify-content: flex-start;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 88%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;\">\n       <div style=\"margin-top: 3px;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;transform: translate3d(-8px, 0px, 0px);text-align: left;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <div style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);text-align: justify;font-size: 20px;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(234, 67, 53);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">2. 结对编程</span></strong></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjclsq4o21e8\">如今 CSS 已经非常强大了。但选择过多有时也会让人感到困惑: 我需要的是&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\">align-items</span>&nbsp;吗？还是&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\">justify-items</span>？还是&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\">justify-self</span>&nbsp;或&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\">align-content</span>？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjclsq4o5nz\">有时您清楚地知道想要达成的效果，却始终找不到正确的 CSS 属性组合。下次遇到这种困境时，只需向 AI 阐述您的目标，即可让它为您提供解决方案。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjclsq4ocxe\">AI 辅助功能会分析您现有的代码，将其与您期望实现的效果进行对比，并为您提供所需的修复建议。您可以直接审核、应用，并将其复制到您的代码库中。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);overflow: hidden;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(83, 98, 242, 0);margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-right: 0%;margin-bottom: 3px;margin-left: 0%;text-align: justify;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;height: auto;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(70, 70, 70);background-color: rgba(84, 98, 242, 0);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 4px 0px inset;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;justify-content: flex-start;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 88%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;\">\n       <div style=\"margin-top: 3px;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;transform: translate3d(-8px, 0px, 0px);text-align: left;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <div style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);text-align: le f t;font-size: 20px;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 188, 4);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">3. 无障碍功能顾问</span></strong></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjcna0bm22up\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">确保您的网站能够通过辅助技术访问和使用是至关重要的。</span><span leaf=\"\">您应该在开发之初就充分考虑无障碍功能，并在整个开发过程中遵循&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">Web 内容无障碍指南</span>&nbsp;(WCAG)。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjcna0bm22lm\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);font-size: 12px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjcnandc2ku\"><span leaf=\"\">Web 内容无障碍指南</span></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjcna0bmfq6\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(147, 147, 147);font-size: 12px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjcnandcar6\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/WAI/standards-guidelines/wcag/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.w3.org/WAI/standards-guidelines/wcag/</a></span></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjcm95z41x61\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjcm95zj1w73\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">利用 AI 辅助，您可以获得如何将普通&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\">&lt;div&gt;</span>&nbsp;替换为更具语义化的 HTML 元素、如何恰当使用额外的&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\">aria-*</span>&nbsp;属性，以及如何优化颜色对比度等方面的专业建议。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjclp13naq\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">建议尝试的提示</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjcma6vzqq5\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjcma6wc6il\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\">What about color contrast in this element?</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);overflow: hidden;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(83, 98, 242, 0);margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-right: 0%;margin-bottom: 3px;margin-left: 0%;text-align: justify;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;height: auto;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(70, 70, 70);background-color: rgba(84, 98, 242, 0);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 4px 0px inset;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;justify-content: flex-start;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 88%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;\">\n       <div style=\"margin-top: 3px;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;transform: translate3d(-8px, 0px, 0px);text-align: left;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <div style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);text-align: le f t;font-size: 20px;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 168, 83);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">4. 彰显个性</span></strong></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px